settings.heading: What Kratom is?
settings.text:
Kratom is another beneficial plant. It is called Mitragyna speciosa in scientific language, and it belongs to the coffee family. Kratom grows naturally in Indonesia, Malaysia and some other parts of Southeast Asia.

Kratom leaves have a high alkaloid count which makes it potential. It initiates mild calming and euphoric effects. These effects are less than opiates. The only high dosage of Kratom can induce these effects. In minor quantity, it initiates analgesic and relaxing effects.
